# Monitoring, repair & rerun

The Jobs UI — the exam's monitoring go-to.

- **Run history** — every run + **duration sparkline** → spot **trends** (2× slower than before)
- **Task graph** — single run's DAG by state: 🔴 failed · ⚪ skipped · 🟢 ok → find **upstream blocker**
- **Repair run** — rerun **only failed tasks**, same params/DAG → cheaper, safer
- **Run dashboard / metrics** — success rate, p95 duration (capacity, SLA)

## Exam patterns

- "median duration tripled — look first?" → **run history** (trend) → **task graph** (offending task)
- Late-stage failure → **repair run** (reuse the 5 good tasks, not rerun all 6h)
